    "media:imagetext": "Caroomba, city of the Blue\nMountains in New South Wales,\noffers a trio of eurious crags.\nStanding 1000 feet above the\nJamieson Valley, these \"Three\nSisters' command a sweep of\nred and ochre cliffs . .. mist-\ndeepened bowls of cobalt blue.\nPen American serves the\nSouth Pacific through Nandi\nin the Fiji Islands, Sydney in\nAustralia and through Auckland\nin New Zealand\nThis wens is one of a complete set, suitable for framing,\nwhich may be okaixed by writing to: Serwee Manager,\nPacife- Alaska Dicision, Pan American World Airways,\nInc.. International Airport. San Francisco, California.",
